latestPosts.caption:
Definitely won the friends lottery with these guys. We could be anywhere and have the best time, love watching the kids together and making the best memories 🌴

Also had alot of questions re where we stayed. We had a week in @anda.barutcollection Didim, Turkey. The overall experience was gorgeous, kids were very well entertained, especially in the splash park and the food, pools (4, not including adult pool, one of which was salt water and heated) and rooms were to a very high standard. As we went during half term the hotel was full so we struggled slightly getting into the a la carte restaurants but the staff managed to sort us for a couple of nights. Getting sunbeds was also quite tricky (there was 12 of us) but I find this in any hotel tbh. Overall a lovely trip and I’m sad it’s all over! 

#turkey #travel #travelwithfriends #halfterm #family #memoriesmade #hotelreview #takemeback #tuihotelsturkey

Let’s hope this week is as good as this @farmrio dress
